# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# # MANDATE: Commit messages MUST be in ENGLISH.
# # Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore, perf, ci, revert
# # Scope: api, ui, db, auth, etc.
# # Subject: imperative mood, no period at the end, max 50 characters
#
# [optional body] - explain the WHY, not the what
#
# [optional footer] - Breaking changes, refs #issue
#
# ---
# Example:
# feat(auth): add google oauth provider
#
# Users can now sign in using their Google accounts. 
# Implemented using the passport-google-oauth20 library.
#
# Closes #123
